<Layout title="Pinsky Studio">
  <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="hero" class="py-16">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">
        Recursive Realities
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-8">
        Where algorithmic precision sparks wonder
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          Pinsky's art explores recursive structures and complex systems in
          nature and mathematics, probing the boundaries of perception and time.
          Embracing technology not just as a tool but as a collaborator and even
          a metaphor, Pinsky blends generative algorithms and custom plotter
          hardware with traditional artistic techniques.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          This interplay of the algorithmic and the handmade yields a unique
          fusion of mathematical precision and organic expression, producing
          intricate works that spark curiosity and revelation. Informed by
          computational theory and Constructivist art, and drawing inspiration
          from visionaries such as M.C. Escher, Vera Molnár, Sol LeWitt, and
          Manfred Mohr, Pinsky creates art that invites viewers to reimagine how
          they see reality.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="#gallery"
          class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-white inline-flex items-center gap-x-1"
        >
          Explore Gallery
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- END HERO SECTION -->

    <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
    <section id="about" class="py-10">
      <h2 class="mb-5 text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
        About
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 max-w-2xl">
        Painting in the Latent Space is a groundbreaking art project that
        bridges the gap between technology and traditional art. By leveraging
        custom plotter hardware and algorithmic techniques, each artwork
        transforms hidden mathematical patterns into visually stunning pieces.
        This human–machine collaboration results in a unique blend of digital
        precision and artisanal craftsmanship, inviting you to explore the
        infinite creative possibilities hidden within data.
      </p>
